## Update Template

Update an existing template.

```http
PUT /api/task-templates/:id
```

### Request Body

```json
{
  "name": "Updated Template Name",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "tasks": [...]
}
```

---

## Delete Template

Delete a template.

```http
DELETE /api/task-templates/:id
```

### Example Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "deleted": true,
    "templateId": "template_abc123"
  }
}
```

