## Built-in Templates

Forge includes several built-in templates:

### Bug Fix

```yaml
name: Bug Fix Workflow
tasks:
  - Reproduce bug
  - Fix issue
  - Add regression tests
  - Update changelog
```

### Feature Development

```yaml
name: Feature Development
tasks:
  - Design feature
  - Implement code
  - Write tests
  - Update documentation
```

### Code Review

```yaml
name: Code Review
tasks:
  - Review code quality
  - Check test coverage
  - Verify documentation
  - Approve or request changes
```

### Refactoring

```yaml
name: Refactoring
tasks:
  - Analyze current code
  - Plan refactoring approach
  - Execute refactoring
  - Verify tests pass
```

